              correct: 0,
              explanation: "PV of cash inflows = £12,000 × 3.791 = £45,492. NPV = £45,492 − £40,000 = £5,492. The positive NPV confirms the project earns more than the 10% cost of capital and should be accepted.",
              topic: "NPV",
