              correct: 1,
              explanation: "IRR ≈ L + [NPV_L ÷ (NPV_L − NPV_H)] × (H − L) = 12 + [6,000 ÷ (6,000 + 2,000)] × (18 − 12) = 12 + (6,000 ÷ 8,000) × 6 = 12 + 0.75 × 6 = 12 + 4.5 = 16.5%.",
              topic: "IRR",
