              "Set MR = MC: 140 − 4Q = 20 → 4Q = 120 → Q* = 30 units",
              "Find P*: P* = 140 − 2(30) = 140 − 60 = £80",
              "TR: £80 × 30 = £2,400",
              "TC: (£20 × 30) + £800 = £600 + £800 = £1,400",
